name: Bell-Borne Geocheloner
description: Activate the protection of Bell-Borne Geochelone, dealing Glacio DMG to nearby enemies based on current character's DEF. Reduce incoming damage, increase damage dealt.

name: Dreamless
description: Transform into Dreamless to continuously attack enemies and deal Havoc DMG. This Echo Skill deals more damage after Rover-Havoc casts their Resonance Liberation.

name: Crownless
description: Transform into Crownless and relentlessly assault enemies, dealing Havoc DMG. Increase current character's Havoc DMG and Resonance Skill DMG.

name: Feilian Beringalr
description: Transform into Feilian Beringal to continuously attack enemies, dealing Aero DMG. Increase current character's Aero DMG and Heavy Attack DMG.

name: Impermanence Heronr
description: Transform into Impermanence Heron to deal Havoc DMG. Long press to spit flames and continuously deal Havoc DMG. Once the attacks hit any enemy, restore current character's Resonance Energy. Increase next character's damage dealt.

name: Inferno Riderr
description: Transform into Inferno Rider to perform consecutive strikes, dealing Fusion DMG. Increase current character's Fusion DMG and Basic Attack DMG. Long press Echo Skill to enter the Riding Mode.

name: Lampylumen Myriadr
description: Transform into Lampylumen Myriad to continuously attack enemies, dealing Glacio damage. Increase current character's Glacio DMG and Resonance Skill DMG.

name: Mech Abominationr
description: Deal Electro DMG to enemies nearby and create Mech Waste that explodes in a while. Increase current character's ATK.

name: Mourning Aixr
description: Transform into Mourning Aix to continuously attack enemies, dealing Spectro damage. Increase current character's Spectro DMG and Resonance Liberation DMG.

name: Tempest Mephisr
description: Transform into Tempest Mephis to continuously attack enemies, dealing Electro damage. Increase current character's Electro DMG & Heavy Attack DMG.

name: Thundering Mephisr
description: Transform into Thundering Mephis to deal Electro DMG. Increase the current character's Electro DMG and Resonance Liberation DMG.

name: Autopuppet Scout
description: Transform into Autopuppet Scout, to deal Glacio DMG to enemies nearby and generate Ice Walls.

name: Chaserazor
description: Transform into Carapace to perform spinning attacks, dealing Aero DMG.

name: Chasm Guardian
description: Transform into Chasm Guardian to perform a powerful strike that deals Havoc DMG. Lose some HP on hit and then recover HP over time.

name: Cyan-Feathered Heron
description: Transform into Cyan-Feathered Heron to charge at the enemies, dealing Aero DMG and interrupt enemy Special Skill.

name: Flautist
description: Transform into a Flautist to deal Electro DMG and recover Concerto Energy on hit.

name: Geohide Saurian
description: Summon a Viridblaze Saurian to continuously spit fire, dealing Fusion DMG.

name: Havoc Dreadmane
description: Transform into a Havoc Dreadmane to launch tail strikes, dealing Havoc DMG.

name: Hoochief
description: Transform into Hoochief Cyclone to deal Aero DMG.

name: Rocksteady Guardian
description: Transform into the Rocksteady Guardian to enter a Parry Stance. Counterattack when hit by Special Skill to interrupt enemy Special Skills and deal Spectro DMG based on Max HP.

name: Roseshroom
description: Summon a Roseshroom to fire a laser, and deal Havoc DMG.

name: Spearback
description: Summon a Spearback to perform continuous claw strikes, dealing Physical DMG.

name: Stonewall Bracer
description: Transform into Stonewall Bracer and charge forward. Successful hits grant a follow-up strike and a shield.

name: Tambourinist
description: Summon a Tambourinist to let friendly units inflict additional Havoc DMG.

name: Violet-Feathered Heron
description: Transform into Violet-Feathered Heron to block enemy attacks. Counterattack to deal Electro DMG and recover Concerto Energy.

name: Aero Predator
description: Summon an Aero Predator to deal Aero DMG.

name: Chirpuff
description: Summon a Chirpuff to blast a powerful gust of wind. Deals Aero DMG and knocks enemies back.

name: Cruisewing
Possible Sonata Effects: Celestial Light Rejuvenating Glow Moonlit Clouds
description: Summon a Cruisewing to heal friendly units.

name: Diamondclaw
description: Transform into Diamondclaw to enter a Defense Stance. Counterattack to deal Physical DMG.

name: Electro Predator
description: Summon an Electro Predator to fire a rain of arrows, dealing Electro DMG.

name: Excarat
description: Transform into Excarat to quickly advance and become immune to damage.

name: Fission Junrock
Possible Sonata Effects: Void Thunder Rejuvenating Glow Moonlit Clouds
description: Summon a Fission Junrock for healing. If not in combat, it picks up minerals or plants nearby for you.

name: Fusion Dreadmane
description: Summon a Fusion Dreadmane to fiercely strike the enemies, dealing Fusion DMG.

name: Fusion Prism
Possible Sonata Effects: Freezing Frost Molten Rift Lingering Tunes
description: Summon a Fusion Prism that deals Fusion DMG with crystal shards.

name: Fusion Warrior
Possible Sonata Effects: Molten Rift Void Thunder Sierra Gale
description: Transform into Fusion Warrior to block enemy attacks. Deal Fusion DMG and reduce this Echo Skill's CD when the block is successful.

name: Glacio Predator
description: Summon a Glacio Predator to throw ice spears and deal Glacio DMG.

name: Glacio Prism
Possible Sonata Effects: Freezing Frost Sun-sinking Eclipse Moonlit Clouds
description: Summon a Glacio Prism that deals Glacio DMG with crystal shards.

name: Gulpuff
description: Summon a Gulpuff to blow bubbles and cause Glacio damage.

name: Havoc Prism
Possible Sonata Effects: Void Thunder Celestial Light Sun-sinking Eclipse
description: Summon a Havoc Prism that deals Havoc DMG with crystal shards.

name: Havoc Warrior
description: Transform into a Havoc Warrior to continuously deal Havoc DMG.

name: Hoartoise
description: Transform into a Hoartoise and slowly restore HP.

name: Hooscamp
description: Transform into Hooscamp Flinger and pounce, dealing Aero DMG.

name: Sabyr Boar
Possible Sonata Effects: Freezing Frost Sierra Gale Moonlit Clouds
description: Summon a Sabyr Boar to charge and deal Physical DMG.

name: Snip Snap
Possible Sonata Effects: Molten Rift Rejuvenating Glow Lingering Tunes
description: Summon a Snip Snap that throws fireballs, dealing Fusion DMG.

name: Spectro Prism
Possible Sonata Effects: Molten Rift Void Thunder Celestial Light
description: Summon a Spectro Prism that deals Spectro DMG with laser.

name: Tick Tack
Possible Sonata Effects: Sun-sinking Eclipse Rejuvenating Glow Lingering Tunes
description: Summon a Tick Tack that deals Havoc DMG and reduces enemy Vibration Strength.

name: Traffic Illuminator
Possible Sonata Effects: Molten Rift Void Thunder Sierra Gale
description: Summon a Traffic Illuminator to immobilize the enemies.

name: Vanguard Junrock
Possible Sonata Effects: Void Thunder Rejuvenating Glow Lingering Tunes
description: Summon a Vanguard Junrock that charges forward, dealing Physical DMG to enemies in its path.

name: Whiff Whaff
Possible Sonata Effects: Sierra Gale Rejuvenating Glow Moonlit Clouds
description: Summon a Whiff Whaff that deals Aero DMG and produces a Low-pressure Zone.

name: Young Geohide Saurian
Possible Sonata Effects: Molten Rift Void Thunder Lingering Tunes
description: Transform into a Baby Viridblaze Saurian, rest in place to restore HP.

name: Young Roseshroom
description: Summon a Baby Roseshroom to fire a laser, and deal Havoc DMG.

name: Zig Zag
Possible Sonata Effects: Celestial Light Moonlit Clouds Lingering Tunes
description: Summon a Zig Zag that deals Spectro DMG, and creates a Stagnation Zone.
